// Grid composition demo
---

<div class="flow flow-space-md">
    <h2>Grid Composition</h2>
    <p>
        The grid composition creates responsive grid layouts with consistent
        gaps. Items automatically wrap and maintain equal spacing.
    </p>

    <h3>Small Gap Grid</h3>
    <div class="grid-auto grid-gap-sm">
        <div class="card">
            <h4>Card 1</h4>
            <p>This is a grid item with small gaps.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h4>Card 2</h4>
            <p>Another grid item with consistent spacing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h4>Card 3</h4>
            <p>Grid items automatically wrap to new rows.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h3>Medium Gap Grid</h3>
    <div class="grid-auto">
        <div class="card">
            <h4>Feature 1</h4>
            <p>Medium gaps provide more breathing room.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h4>Feature 2</h4>
            <p>Perfect for feature grids and galleries.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h3>Large Gap Grid</h3>
    <div class="grid-auto grid-gap-lg">
        <div class="card">
            <h4>Large Spacing</h4>
            <p>Maximum space between grid items.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h4>Generous Layout</h4>
            <p>Ideal for prominent content sections.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h3>2 Column Grid (Not grid auto)</h3>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2">
        <div class="card">
            <h4>Column 1 Column 1 Column 1 Column 1 Column 1 Column 1</h4>
            <p>This is the first column.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h4>Column 2</h4>
            <p>This is the second column.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h4>Column 2</h4>
            <p>This is the second column.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h4>Column 2</h4>
            <p>This is the second column.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
